FileManager Provides functionality to query and modify Mac-specific file attributes.
 

Package com.apple.eio Description

Provides classes to allow you to take advantage of functionality of the underlying Mac OS X operating system. The classes in this package provide access to features of Mac OS X that may or may not be present on other platforms. It should be noted that depending on any of these features ties Java applications to Mac OS X. For more thorough explanation of some of the topics discussed here, please refer to Inside Mac OS X: System Overview.
